Subject: Fw: [T2] How does one aquire H20 in gastank?

You may want to drop the tank to inspect it.  These tanks are prone to rust
out in their top center where there's a "valley" that's perfect for
collecting water-retaining "stuff."  There's also some seals and hoses up on
top of the tank that could go bad, allowing in water that gets up there.
